sections.heading: to 34-12-6 - Repealed.Section 34-12-7 to 34-12-12 - Repealed.
sections.text: Repeals.— Laws 1981, ch. 305, § 8, repealed 34-12-1 to 34-12-6 NMSA 1978, as enacted by Laws 1969, ch. 209, §§ 1 to 6, and amended by Laws 1973, ch. 212, § 1, Laws 1977, ch. 247, § 147, and Laws 1979, ch. 103, § 1, relating to the judicial council, effective July 1, 1981.

sections.heading: to 34-12-12 - Repealed.
sections.text: Repeals.— Laws 1986, ch. 66, § 2 repealed 34-12-7 to 34-12-12 NMSA 1978, as enacted by Laws 1981, ch. 305, § 2 and amended by Laws 1983, ch. 71, § 1, relating to the judicial council, effective July 1, 1986.
